PROVOST Jim Todd has pledged his support for Samaritans Ayrshire over the next two years. Provost in vow to back Samaritans PROVOST Jim Todd has pledged his support for Samaritans Ayrshire over the next two years.The Kilmarnock-based branch of the charity is now the East Ayrshire provost's chosen charity and has vowed to raise awareness, funds and help them in their vital work.Provost Todd said: &quot;My main aim is to raise awareness, funds and assist them in the work they do to help people when they need it most.&quot; 